<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Activities</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f9fc;
            color: #333;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .about-container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 50px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            background-color: #fff;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            border-radius: 8px;
        }
        .about-title {
            font-size: 2em;
            color: #28A745;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .about-content {
            font-size: 1.2em;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .activities-list {
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .activities-list h3 {
            font-size: 1.5em;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .activities {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .activities li {
            margin: 5px 0;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="about-container">
        <h1 class="about-title">About Activities</h1>
        <p class="about-content">
            Extracurricular activities are an integral part of student life, offering opportunities for learning, collaboration, and personal growth outside the classroom. Our system organizes a wide range of activities to cater to diverse student interests, making it easy to participate and contribute.
        </p>
        <div class="activities-list">
            <h3>Our Activities</h3>
            <ul class="activities">
                <li>Sports and Athletics</li>
                <li>Art and Cultural Clubs</li>
                <li>Science and Technology Groups</li>
                <li>Music and Dance Ensembles</li>
                <li>Debates and Public Speaking</li>
                <li>Community Service and Outreach</li>
                <li>Workshops and Seminars</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <p class="about-content">
            These activities are designed to help students develop their skills, foster teamwork, and build lasting connections. Join us in creating memorable experiences and achieving your personal and academic goals.
        </p>
    </div>
